Only Pull Day Workout You’ll Ever Need
Back, biceps, and rear delts absolutely destroyed in this session!
Started with pull-ups to failure, then hit close-grip lat pulldowns with strict form and deep stretch. Followed by seated rows, rear delt flys, and finished with an intense bicep routine—dumbbell curls, hammer curls, and preacher curls to failure.

Perfect for muscle growth, bigger arms, and that wide V-tapered back.
This is how you build a complete upper body.

Save this pull workout and try it on your next training day!
